snippet.title: A MAZE. / Berlin 2023 | Fantasia Malware presents SEX! At Alexanderplatz
snippet.description:
SEX! At Alexanderplatz is a performance and dating game set in hell (Alexanderplatz).
Crank the lever of your dating app, let the slot machine spin, let sparks of fury fly, let lonely hearts die (alone).

by Fantasia Malware (https://fantasia-malware.net/)

============
ANIMATION: Nomi (https://www.thenomi.com/)
SOUND & MUSIC: Oda Tilset (https://www.noknokaudio.com/)
STREAMING / PRODUCTION: IN THEORY GmbH (https://intheory.events/)
FESTIVAL DESIGN: Form Und Konzept (https://formundkonzept.de/)
